            ADVANCED FORMULA &nbsp; HIGH-PERFORMANCE <br>
            VISIBLE RESULTS
          </p>
          <div class="mt-[1.125rem] large:mt-6">
            <a
              class="button button--primary button--icon min-w-[8.875rem] justify-center"
              role="link"
              aria-disabled="true"
              href="https://tursian.com/collections/all"
            >
              <div class="button__label">
                <span>DISCOVER MORE</span>
                <span class="absolute top-10 left-0"> DISCOVER MORE </span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="slide">
        <img
          class="mobile"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0844/4670/7990/files/Y-4_4.jpg?v=1736760215"
          alt="Slide 2"
        >

        <img
          class="desktop"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0844/4670/7990/files/product_demo_img.jpg?v=1737546169"
          alt="Slide 2"
        >
      </div>

      <div class="slide">
        <img
          class="mobile"
